{"id": 1771, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都看穿了明星们哪些“靠业务水平”之外的吸粉方式？", "description": "为了涨粉，你们可真是各种花招都想得出来呢。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 16127, "comment_count": 69, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170707165617KUcZkwijvA0d9DVs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-09T17:00:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 2519, "title": "现如今你都看穿了明星们哪些“靠业务水平”之外的吸粉方式？", "content": "现如今你都看穿了明星们哪些“靠业务水平”之外的吸粉方式？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 217271, "content": "靠晒马甲线。想塑造自律努力的形象，这招最好使", "image": "img/option/option/20170629171714iJk76yDNWfQjdlte.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217272, "content": "靠厨艺，来自江湖宣传或者上综艺节目，展现居家好男/女人形象", "image": "img/option/option/20170629172051RrIybjeSn6kd3q5s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217273, "content": "靠狼人杀，展现所谓“高智商高情商”", "image": "img/option/option/20170629172334OVJhumsF2WoSfz6X.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217274, "content": "靠写段子，展现“风趣幽默”的另一面", "image": "img/option/option/20170629172530sl08uLCnrMoWkI3f.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217275, "content": "靠拍摄抖音秒拍之类的短视频，跳社会摇，显得很接地气", "image": "img/option/option/20170629172752dyz6CJL8jFxMaPBA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217301, "content": "靠练字和书摘，展现“文化人”人设", "image": "img/option/option/20170629174408jKNUFnlirs05Hvbx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217302, "content": "靠卖腐或炒 cp，进行捆绑销售吸 cp 粉", "image": "img/option/option/20170629175813wtvhWj5la1pYkU37.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 217327, "content": "靠和宠物互动，显得性格温柔且有爱心和耐心", "image": "img/option/option/20170629180806EsMp2haXx8FH5J7G.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}